msgid "Personal data about ancestors, family members, and other persons"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:12
msgid ""
"Personal data about living persons is also stored for the purpose of family history and genealogical research; "
"see inventory data and content data above."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:14
msgid ""
"Family history and genealogical research is a legitimate interest under Article 6(1), first sentence, point "
"(f) of the General Data Protection Regulation (EU GDPR)."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:16
msgid "Family history and genealogical research is the legitimate purpose for processing this data."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:18
msgid ""
"Personal data that you find on this website, such as names, e-mail addresses, photos, addresses, or life "
"dates, is used only for family history and genealogical research and is kept securely."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:19
msgid ""
"Genealogical data is stored for the long term because it is historically relevant and should remain preserved "
"and accessible for future generations."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:20
msgid "Requests for deletion are reviewed individually."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:22
msgid ""
"Deletion may be restricted if further processing is necessary for historical research purposes and deletion "
"would likely make these purposes impossible or seriously impair them, in accordance with Article 17(3)(d) GDPR."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:28
msgid ""
"In addition to the General Data Protection Regulation (EU GDPR), German national data protection rules may "
"apply, in particular the Federal Data Protection Act (BDSG)."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:33
msgid "Legal bases for processing"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:36
msgid "The legal bases for processing personal data depend on the respective processing operation."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:37
msgid ""
"The provision and secure operation of this website, the protection of living persons, and family history "
"research are based on legitimate interests under Article 6(1), first sentence, point (f) GDPR."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:38
msgid ""
"Processing related to user accounts, registered access, and communication with registered users may also be "
"based on contractual or pre-contractual relationships under Article 6(1), first sentence, point (b) GDPR."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:39
msgid ""
"If consent is requested for individual processing operations, the legal basis is Article 6(1), first sentence, "
"point (a) GDPR."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-categories.phtml:40
msgid ""
"Where legal obligations require processing or retention, the legal basis is Article 6(1), first sentence, "
"point (c) GDPR."
