#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:47
msgid "Data protection in connection with online genealogies"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:53
msgid ""
"I am a strong advocate of data protection and would like to emphasize that I naturally make every effort to "
"comply with the GDPR."
msgid_plural ""
"We are strong advocates of data protection and would like to emphasize that we naturally make every effort to "
"comply with the GDPR."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:55
msgid ""
"I am a strong advocate of data protection and would like to emphasize that I naturally make every effort to "
"comply with applicable data protection requirements."
msgid_plural ""
"We are strong advocates of data protection and would like to emphasize that we naturally make every effort to "
"comply with applicable data protection requirements."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:57
msgid ""
"However, fully and clearly legally compliant implementation in all cases is probably not possible in the field "
"of online genealogy."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:58
msgid "Too many questions are disputed and leave room for legal interpretation."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:62
msgid "However, I can rule out with certainty that everyone entered in this family tree knows about it."
msgid_plural "However, we can rule out with certainty that everyone entered in this family tree knows about it."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:63
msgid "Creating a family tree works differently."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:64
msgid "Usually, information about a branch of the family is obtained from one person in that branch."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:65
msgid ""
"I have not obtained verifiable consent from our relatives to enter the respective family in this family tree."
msgid_plural ""
"We have not obtained verifiable consent from our relatives to enter the respective family in this family tree."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:70
msgid ""
"In my opinion, full compliance with the GDPR would therefore only be possible if I took large parts of this "
"family tree offline again."
msgid_plural ""
"In our opinion, full compliance with the GDPR would therefore only be possible if we took large parts of this "
"family tree offline again."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:72
msgid ""
"In my opinion, full compliance with every possible privacy expectation would therefore only be possible if I "
"took large parts of this family tree offline again."
msgid_plural ""
"In our opinion, full compliance with every possible privacy expectation would therefore only be possible if we "
"took large parts of this family tree offline again."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:74
msgid ""
"This, however, would remove the ability of the target group to use it and find their own paths through the "
"extended kinship network."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:76
msgid ""
"I therefore continue to provide the data online on the basis of legitimate interests in family history and "
"historical research."
msgid_plural ""
"We therefore continue to provide the data online on the basis of legitimate interests in family history and "
"historical research."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:77
msgid ""
"The GDPR expressly recognizes that personal data may also be processed for historical research purposes, "
"subject to appropriate safeguards."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:79
msgid ""
"I therefore continue to provide the data online in the interest of family history and historical research."
msgid_plural ""
"We therefore continue to provide the data online in the interest of family history and historical research."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:81
msgid ""
"The data is handled carefully, and objections or requests for restriction or deletion are reviewed "
"individually."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/page/sections/data-rights.phtml:82
msgid ""
"I would therefore like to agree on the following procedure with all users of our website, hoping that this "
"will satisfy the law:"
msgid_plural ""
